Package: NMCleaner
Title: Provides sets of simplified tools to clean and analyse NMC data.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Brian", "Brummer", , "brianb@nicd.ac.za", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4626-416X"))
Description: 
    Assist NMC users to conduct standardised data management, 
    wrangling and analysis of NMC data. 
    The package is designed to ingest raw NMC data form the linelist 
    export function on the NMC web-based application. 
    The package include sample data [`sample'] aswell 
    as shape files for administration boundaries and collated Mid-Year-Population-Estimates. 
